snippet.title: Best VGM 2080 - Super Runabout - Candy ~Blues for M~
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Dreamcast
Super Runabout (2000)
Candy ~Blues for M~
The Surf Coasters (Shigeo Naka)
